overview.en: AFA (Africahead Ipparts) is a brand token listed on Ipparts Exchange (IPPAEX). The token is contractually backed by 48% of the Africahead brand value. AFA raises funds for Africahead business.
overview.zh: AFA (Africahead Ipparts) 是在 Ipparts Exchange (IPPAEX) 上市的品牌代币。该代币由 Africahead 品牌价值的 48% 提供合同支持。 AFA 为 Africahead 业务筹集资金
